{"tid":2266523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"從1942到2019 香港淪陷前世今生  美導演燃重光希望","createTime":"2020-11-01T11:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T19:46:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f7c9abbd35da81bdb9e8d5c64dcf926bcbc95c","tid":2266523,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:25:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/3SOYAZN5FFGDPDEY6BMB64B6WI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2F3SOYAZN5FFGDPDEY6BMB64B6WI%2F&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnhyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=6e5afa01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2F3SOYAZN5FFGDPDEY6BMB64B6WI%2F&h=75bdcb52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/3SOYAZN5FFGDPDEY6BMB64B6WI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n從1942到2019 香港淪陷前世今生 <br />\n美導演燃重光希望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sCRpa9UHc5f-brgskWP2qew0jKU=/3150x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EORDHWKJKBEZHERH4ORLSAUN7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsCRpa9UHc5f-brgskWP2qew0jKU%3D%2F3150x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEORDHWKJKBEZHERH4ORLSAUN7A.jpg&h=866072b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美籍獨立電影導演Craig McCourry拍攝《香港1942──柳暗花明淪陷時》遇上不少阻滯，幸好一眾支持者願意為他張羅。<br />\n<br />\n「終有一日，香港會再重光。」以香港為基地，美籍獨立電影導演Craig McCourry再推新戲，亦是2018年他執導「香港保衞戰」題材電影《1941的聖誕》的續集──電影《香港1942──柳暗花明淪陷時》。預告片已在YouTube發佈，故事講述二戰時一對兄妹在皇軍入侵時，走難到香港的經歷。香港淪陷的悲劇，過去年多飽受暴政摧殘的香港人應不會陌生。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：香港角度出發 第二套保衞戰電影<br />\n<br />\n記者：葉親惠<br />\n<br />\n電影講述主角兄妹走難來港隨即遇上香港淪陷，皇軍在香港的鐵腕管治一。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e1PMUShWlP6RBX_thihk_knPaLM=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IQGQNC2IVZECPFE3YNIKGLDVAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe1PMUShWlP6RBX_thihk_knPaLM%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIQGQNC2IVZECPFE3YNIKGLDVAM.jpg&h=d9a9405d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃婉華飾演的陳玲，在電影的最後一刻說到「Someday Hong Kong will be free again」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1WO4kkapdTYOuOAPssV72P5owHo=/3150x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M4CCZWRVLBF3XAHEJQ6X24SVHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1WO4kkapdTYOuOAPssV72P5owHo%3D%2F3150x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM4CCZWRVLBF3XAHEJQ6X24SVHY.jpg&h=82c0ddf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女主角從上海逃難到香港，豈料因淪陷而要再次面對去留問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「Hong Kong will be free again」<br />\n<br />\n導演兼編劇McCourry表示，劇本早於2018年至2019年初已完成初稿，但是戲中對白，例如「Someday Hong Kong will be free again」一句，就是啟發自2019年的抗爭，「我們拍攝當晚（2019年11月），劇組人員當然有被正在香港發生的事（抗爭）影響到情感，劇本上原有另一句對白，但與演員等討論後，將該段對白改成現在的（Someday Hong Kong will be free again）看來更加適合，以表達為香港帶一點希望」。<br />\n<br />\nMcCourry說，對白是希望為在1942年淪陷、黑暗的香港找出一個對。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港」（Free Hong Kong）口號自今年7月後已成為香港敏感詞，McCourry不希。。。。。。。。。，如果沒有自由，將會是個很黑暗的世界。」<br />\n<br />\n對白除了為反映香港淪陷時的情況，某些元素仍可與今日的香港比較，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。短缺演變成的飢餓，迫使港人離開，因為他們（日軍）不想養活港人，日軍想香港人口減少以方便管治」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6BZTXSn3-FF5KmUfjoUhGZsB-pI=/2363x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QN5HSSPBWNBTZJ7K7WDWS5D3IU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6BZTXSn3-FF5KmUfjoUhGZsB-pI%3D%2F2363x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQN5HSSPBWNBTZJ7K7WDWS5D3IU.jpg&h=57d912e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■McCourry特邀這台英軍電單車的主人為他拍了幾場戲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩代同一抉擇：怎樣離開<br />\n<br />\n走難故事是《香港1942》其中一條主線，亦反映出當時港人面對是否移民的兩難困局，角色陳玲就要面對去留問題。McCourry說：「主角陳玲（由黃婉華飾演）面對的困局是想在世界上尋找一個安全的居所，她首先由上海逃難到香港，但香港淪陷時，她又再要逃難。這個主題正正是《香港1942》想要突出的。」<br />\n<br />\n1942年的港人面對相同的抉擇：怎樣離開香港、走難到何處。正因McCourry。。。。。。。。。。。。，但他們的確是啟發自真人真事，而當時的歷史背景亦都是寫實的。」<br />\n<br />\n《香港1942》預計本月內完成後期製作，並會參加11月9日至13日在洛杉磯舉行的美國電影市場影展，亦正安排於明年在香港放映，一切都很視乎疫情的發展。"},{"pid":"39c171ebb3a49d5bf93b77a1ee0d00c77f9361e6","tid":2266523,"uid":9640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T12:14:39.000Z","msg":"岩岩都睇到<br />\n之後去咗Youtube搵條Trailer <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kf0GxCv4TeE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKf0GxCv4TeE&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnhyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=5bd47108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kf0GxCv4TeE</a><br />\n<br />\n個感覺幾特別<br />\n好舊片風格"},{"pid":"e6f23f7349b846a829bb00e6c81753092584803c","tid":2266523,"uid":29796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T12:17:11.000Z","msg":"感激為我拍紀錄片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac6cb7533d49b986e9a456fc3782bbad0d615d0","tid":2266523,"uid":234974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"老實講, 佢上套咩1941 唔算得上係咩電影, 仲渣過大學學生習作, 我只會當佢係 rennactment record video <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39995cfb82c8ac9d72f4572198e325c827e92979","tid":2266523,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ac6cb7533d49b986e9a456fc3782bbad0d615d0","tid":2266523,"uid":234974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"老實講, 佢上套咩1941 唔算得上係咩電影, 仲渣過大學學生習作, 我只會當佢係 renn